**What is your understanding of DevOps and Cloud Engineering?**

= DevOps is a culture and set of practices that bridges the gap between software development (Dev) and IT operations (Ops) .

= Devops follow some principles like Collaboration , Automation, Security , Monitoring , Feedback .

**Why you are starting learning DevOps & Cloud?**

= I am starting DevOps because it tech me how to automate things , how to build CI/CD pipeline for how to line up things and collaborations .

= DevOps engineers are in high demand because every company wants faster, more reliable software delivery.

**Where do you want to reach?**

= My aim is to become a professional who can bridge AI development with DevOps .

**How you will stay consistent every single day?**

= i will stay consistent everyday by following the routine , setting some some goal that i can achieve and track my progress .
